(216, 1, '2013-08-30 05:29:55', '2013-08-30 05:29:55', 'Graphic design is a creative process, one most often involving a client and a designer, and traditionally completed in conjunction with producers of form (printers, sign makers, etc.). Graphic design is undertaken to convey a specific message (or messages) to a targeted audience, usually from the client, known as the ''brief''. The term "graphic design" can also refer to a number of artistic and professional disciplines that focus on visual communication and presentation.', 'Graphics', 'Graphic design is a creative process, one most often involving a client and a designer, and traditionally completed in conjunction with producers of form (printers, sign makers, etc.). Graphic design is undertaken to convey a specific message (or messages) to a targeted audience, usually from the client, known as the ''brief''. The term "graphic design" can also refer to a number of artistic and professional disciplines that focus on visual communication and presentation.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'graphics', '', '', '2013-08-30 05:29:55', '2013-08-30 05:29:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/photography/?post_type=product&#038;p=216', 0, 'product', '', 0, '49'),
